{
  "stem": "1363.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were-- one of them were the Jewish Nyilas in the uniform-- took these inmates and took them to the ghetto, and they were freed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's exactly what I meant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's how they got rescued.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It's getting heavy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we-- when the Russians came in to that part of the city, where I was in that protected house, I was so happy to see the Russians, that they're coming closer.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a street fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was actually from one building to another, and from one street to the other, and I joined them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, hundreds.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hundreds.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, maybe in where I was, in the cellar there in that protected house, there were about 50, and in the next house was 50.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were all scattered around because there were quite a lot of protected house in that area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that was liberation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, we got liberated-- if-- I can't remember if it were 14th or 16th.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I marched with them, street-fighting, to get, as soon as possible, to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, that was one of the incidents where I got caught by three Russian soldiers, and by gunpoint, they took me up in an apartment, which was bombarded, the glasses were out of the house, because there was not one house in Budapest which had the glasses in it.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they [INAUDIBLE] raped me then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was something which I am surprised, that now, with my old age, I didn't have any hang-ups, human beings-wise, or sexually, or anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I only know that I begged them to leave me alone because, I said, doctor, doctor.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
